    <h2>About William Greiner</h2>
 

  <p>William Greiner was born in New Orleans on September 8th, 1957. He holds an MBA from Suffolk University in Boston, and a BFA in photography from Tufts University. Greiner has held countless solo and group exhibitions, and his work can be found in as many public collections and publications around America and Europe.</p>

